[SN]TITLE[SN]
Kirkpatrick-Fleming flat cap motorway walker mystery

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Police have appealed for information after an elderly man in a tweed jacket and a flat cap was reported walking along a motorway in southern Scotland.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened at about 10:50 on the A74(M) at Kirkpatrick Fleming.
The man was reported to be walking south along the hard shoulder but police patrols found no trace of him.
They are keen to speak to anyone who saw the man.
